<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head><meta charset="utf-8"><title>股票推荐</title></head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;font-family:{{ font_family }};background:#f5f5f5;">
<div style="max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;background:#fff;padding:20px;">
  <div style="border-bottom:2px solid #2c3e50;padding-bottom:10px;margin-bottom:14px;">
    <h1 style="margin:0;font-size:20px;color:#2c3e50;">🎯 股票推荐</h1>
    <div style="font-size:12px;color:#999;">{{ date }} · {{ data_time_label }} {{ data_time }}</div>
  </div>

  <div style="background:#fff8e1;border:1px solid #ffe082;border-radius:6px;padding:10px;margin-bottom:14px;font-size:12px;color:#8d6e00;">
    ⚠️ 免责声明:本邮件为量化选股<b>跟踪信号</b>,非投资建议。量化模型基于历史规律,不预测未来。投资有风险,决策请自行判断。
  </div>

  <div class="summary-box" style="background:#f8f9fa;border-radius:8px;padding:14px;margin-bottom:14px;">
    {{ picks_brief }}
  </div>

  {{ picks_sections }}

  <div style="margin-top:18px;padding-top:10px;border-top:1px solid #eee;font-size:11px;color:#aaa;">
    {{ disclaimer }}<br>数据源:akshare / yfinance · {{ generated_by }} · {{ generated_at }}
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
